Detailed Description

template<class RealType = double>
class boost::random::normal_distribution_v156< RealType >

Instantiations of class template normal_distribution_v156 model a . Such a distribution produces random numbers x distributed with probability density function , where mean and sigma are the parameters of the distribution.
